Tom Segura and Bert Kreischer’s podcast 2 Bears 1 Cave was already losing steam before the comedians suddenly disappeared for six weeks. When they finally returned.. fans realized how disconnected and lazy the show had become. Instead of addressing the backlash, they brushed it off, leaving their once massive podcast on the brink of collapse.
